{"comments":"Static HTML Rendering Target\n\nRenders Hydrogen Elements to static HTML strings for:\n- Server-side rendering (SSR)\n- Static site generation (SSG)\n- HTML email generation\n- Testing and debugging\n\n## Design Principles\n\nEvent handlers are IGNORED in static output because:\n- Static HTML has no runtime to execute handlers\n- Handlers are wired up separately when hydrating client-side\n- This matches the Elm/Halogen SSR model\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Render.Element as E\nimport Hydrogen.Target.Static as TS\n\nhtml :: String\nhtml = TS.render (E.div_ [ E.class_ \"container\" ] [ E.text \"Hello\" ])\n-- \"<div class=\\\"container\\\">Hello</div>\"\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render an Element to an HTML string with default options\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvisible"},"tag":"ForAll"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Target/Static.purs","start":[87,1]},"title":"render"},{"children":[],"comments":"Render an Element to an HTML string with custom options\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Target","Static"],"RenderOptions"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotatio